  "subject": "Investigating the build with netconf-executor, test commit.",
  "commit_message": "Investigating the build with netconf-executor, test commit.\n\nIssue-ID: CCSDK-1126\n\nrev4: Sped up the test build by removing cds-ui,components from pom, as well as all tests\nrev5: put back the refactoring for data objects (NetconfMessage, NetconfSessionListenerImpl)\nrev6: put back refactored NetconfDevice, NetconfSessionImpl\nrev7: put back refactored NetconfSessionListener, NetconfDeviceCommunicator, NetconfSessionListenerImpl, NetconfSshClientWrapper\nrev8: put back new netconf-executor tests\nrev9: refactoring: removed 'checkAndReestablish' unused method (not needed)\nrev10: put back original cds tests: controllerblueprints, blueprint-core blueprint-scripts, blueprint-validation/resource-dict tests\nrev11: just a test\nrev12: put back original cds tests: cli-executor, resource-resolution and restconf-executor tests, and one test I forgot to include in netconf-executor tests - NetconfSessionListenerImplTest\nrev13: just a test\nrev14: removing NetconfSessionListenerImplTest test\nChange-Id: I6c87382dd609f9cdddcc0311dc6759ee108305f3\nSigned-off-by: Oleg Mitsura <oleg.mitsura@amdocs.com>\n",
